                            <comment id="13526657" author="hustlmsp" created="Fri, 7 Dec 2012 19:01:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks Flavio.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;several comments:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;+| @inter_region_ssl_enabled@ | Enables SSL across regions. Default is false. |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This setting is not recommended. Users are suggested to enable cross region ssl connections in conf/hw_region_client.conf&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;+| @password@ | Sets the password used for BookKeeper ledgers. Default is the empty string. |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this password setting is for ssl cert file not for bookkeeper. currently we had a hardcode &apos;silly&apos; password in Hedwig. Do we need a separated jira to expose it as a setting?&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;BTW,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) you might need to refer conf/hw_server.conf as an reference for the documentation.&lt;br/&gt;
2) there is some configurations missed in conf/hw_server.conf after some recent changes. could you help putting them in conf/hw_server.conf too?&lt;br/&gt;
3) do you mind putting the setting about crossing region client settings in this documentation too? you could find them in conf/hw_region_client.conf&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13527153" author="fpj" created="Sat, 8 Dec 2012 14:38:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the review, Sijie.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;This setting is not recommended. Users are suggested to enable cross region ssl connections in conf/hw_region_client.conf&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t know what you want me to say in the textile file, so haven&apos;t done anything about it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;this password setting is for ssl cert file not for bookkeeper. currently we had a hardcode &apos;silly&apos; password in Hedwig.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fixed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do we need a separated jira to expose it as a setting?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maybe so. If no one has actually needed it, then I would leave as is for now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;there is some configurations missed in conf/hw_server.conf after some recent changes. could you help putting them in conf/hw_server.conf too?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve found only three parameters missing. If see you any other parameter missing, please let me know or add it directly and generate a new patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;do you mind putting the setting about crossing region client settings in this documentation too? you could find them in conf/hw_region_client.conf&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Done.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
